OL,3,CBike crash death of 'a loving father
OL,4,Cand partner' leaves family
OL,5,C"heartbroken"
OL,7,FThe family of a man who died in a
OL,8,Fcollision in Rivington have spoken of
OL,9,Ftheir broken hearts in a tribute
OL,10,Freleased through Lancashire Police.
OL,12,F38-year-old Anthony Place, from
OL,13,FHorwich, died at the scene when his
OL,14,Fblue Yamaha motorbike collided with a
OL,15,Fcarpark barrier on a side road off
OL,16,FRivington Lane, near to Rivington Barn.
OL,18,FPolice received reports of the
OL,19,Fcollision just after 9:04 pm on
OL,20,FWednesday 8 April.
