OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1776146706
OL,3,CBike crash death of 'a loving father
OL,4,Cand partner' leaves family
OL,5,C"heartbroken"
OL,7,FHis passenger, a woman in her 30s, was
OL,8,Ftaken to the hospital, but only
OL,9,Fsuffered minor injuries. No other
OL,10,Fvehicles were involved.
OL,12,FThe family said "Rest easy our
OL,13,Fbeautiful son ` you left us way too
OL,14,Fsoon.
OL,16,F"Your smile lit up every room you went
OL,17,Fin to and your energy gravitated on to
OL,18,Feveryone you met.
OL,26,@tD@QOUxD@AOU
