FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1776146706
OL,3,CBike crash death of 'a loving father
OL,4,Cand partner' leaves family
OL,5,C"heartbroken"
OL,7,F"You were a loving father, stepfather,
OL,8,Fand partner, the best big brother, and
OL,9,Fa crazy uncle.
OL,11,F"Words will not come close to how this
OL,12,Femptiness feels. You have left many
OL,13,Fhearts broken and a void that will
OL,14,Fnever be filled."
OL,16,FThe Lancashire Police said the
OL,17,Finvestigation continues and they are
OL,18,Fnow appealing for information and
OL,19,Ffootage that could assist their
OL,20,Fenquiries.
